      "span_text": "We selected the oxaliplatin derivative cis,trans,cis-[Pt(ethanedioato) Cl(2-hydroxyethanolato)(1R,2R-DACH)] (DACH = diaminocyclohexane) as Pt(IV) precursor In addition, the two compounds were massively accumulated in glioma cells (10-to 100-fold enhanced accumulation) and were capable of inducing apoptosis similar to cisplatin  .",
